filament_end_gcode:
; Filament-specific end gcode 
;END gcode for filament
filament_start_gcode:
; Filament gcode
;M412 D10  ;10mm distance
;M412 S1   ; Enable runout
;M900 K0.10 ; Linear advance spring constant -guess

{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*HOTEND_AFTERBURNER_E3D.*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==0.4} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.050{endif}  ; checked 2021-09-09 maybe wrong toolhead
{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*HOTEND_SWITCH_E3D.*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==0.4} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.38{endif}  ; Tested 2022-01-22 Switchwire Bowden
{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*HOTEND_AFTERBURNER_E3D.*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==0.25} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.1275{endif}  ; checked 2022-04-05
{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*HOTEND_AFTERBURNER_REVO.*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==0.4} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.040 {endif}  ; checked 2022-04-23 

SET_VELOCITY_LIMIT VELOCITY=500
SET_VELOCITY_LIMIT ACCEL=4000
SET_VELOCITY_LIMIT ACCEL_TO_DECEL=4000
name: Anycubic PLA Speedtest
